window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It's totally normal to fall in love with an audiobook narrator's voice, right? </p> <p>Right. </p> <p>Just ask Vera, who listens to \"her\" guy whenever and wherever she can: while driving, working, parenting, cooking, cleaning, showering...you name it. </p> <p>But now, she's bringing him into the bedroom. And her husband is less than pleased. </p> <p><i>These Walls Can Talk</i> is a raucous and heartfelt love letter to romance audiobooks: the authors who write them, the narrators and engineers who record them, and the passionate fans who devour them.</p>"; 
